        <content><![CDATA[<p>While the contents referenced in a container page are rendered by so called <a href="%(link0)">formatters</a>, the task of the template JSP is mainly the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>providing an HTML wrapper document common to all web pages</li>
<li>defining the <code>&lt;cms:enable-ade&gt;</code> and at least one <code>&lt;cms:container&gt;</code> tag for activation of content edition</li>
</ul>]]></content>
